description:
Repost from @standup911
•
I am truly blessed to have you all here with on my account. I truly am grateful for your follow and how many of us actually care about the future of our children. I know it might be hard to grasp when you don’t get to see all the engagement via our independent accounts have or how much we have in total but i can tell you that just one of our accounts is more than capable of reaching millions of people weekly or even per post let alone what each awareness account does collectively. What you can see are the eye opening comments being left on these hollyweird, fake doctors who haven’t practiced in 25 yrs, big tech owner’s accounts. I truly believe that if we continue to raise awareness and implement boycotting that we can create massive amounts of change. It’s that simple. All you have to do is open your mouth, support those who are on the front lines speaking, stop supporting the media or corporations and support local businesses. You also have to be mindful of your health and mental clarity as well. 
Much love to everyone who checked out my story highlight 🔒🔑. Again i am grateful for your support, even more so in times like now.
